Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: It's a Nine Ring Circus and You'll Never be Bored
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00szrxz
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 1 Dec 2000
Alistair Cooke examines the voting irregularities of 1876 and applies the lessons learned from them to the current electoral crisis in Florida.